title: Top Floor Studio Apartment With Look&Lease Special!
posting_body: ['Upscale Living in the New Northgate', 'Welcome to Prism – a new upscale apartment experience in the heart of Seattle’s Northgate neighborhood.', 'Prism is built for those looking to make connections with interesting people and the exciting places around them.', 'Here you will enjoy brand new, light-filled apartment living with a boutique feel and rare live/work options.', 'You will connect with a diverse and vibrant community including thriving students, busy professionals, ambitious entrepreneurs, and conscious urbanites.', 'For those looking for truly connected urban living, this is the most brilliant choice.', 'Find your new home at Prism and experience the new Northgate.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 17', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 474 - 536 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Energy-Efficient Windows', '- Microwave', '- Distinct Wood-Style Flooring', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Dishwasher', '- In-wall ports for air conditioners', '- Balconies in select homes', '- Walk-in Closets', 'In select homes', '- Washer/Dryer in apartment', 'Community Amenities', '- Package Lockers', '- Resident Lounge', '- Bike Storage', '- Controlled Access Entry', '- Secluded Courtyard', '- Business Lounge', '- Controlled Access Garage', 'Pet Policy', 'Dog and Cats Allowed.', 'Office Hours', 'Wednesday & Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Tuesday & Thursday 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prism Apartments', '10711 8th Ave NE, Seattle, WA, 98125', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'LrNFqxZ8V']
